    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s still in absolute pristine condition\u2014not a scratch or a smudge to be found. It runs like a dream and looks even better. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a great new owner who will love it as much as I have. Come swing by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
